snippet.title: MixMob Gen0 Masks Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Official MixMob Mask reveal.
Our masks are your identity in the game.
They will evolve as you progress and level up.
We're dropping 10,000 to start the revolution.
Hand crafted by our talented artists, and remixed by a machine.
✊🔥
